WANDERING STAR is a short film starring @__skywalka__ surfing during one of the shittiest winter ever witnessed on the North Shore. The same winter that @paullavoine choose to go for his first time in Hawaii. And even if the conditions were not perfect, Paul really wanted to make a video to highlight the few good waves who broke in the North Shore.
Wandering Star is supposed to be more artistic than a random surf reel on Instagram, we know that the 16:9 is not the best to seduce the algorithm but we think that the footages doesn’t have to be reframed.
So we hope that you gonna enjoy this short video, if you do feel free to share 🤟🏼
🏄🏽‍♂️ @__skywalka__ 
🎥 @paullavoine
